0540e553d1dc"],

Cell["\<\
This Demonstration could be useful in evaluating the maximum medically \
permissible uncertainty of measurement of a diagnostic test. For example, in \
the the snapshots the population data describe a bimodal distribution of \
serum glucose measurements in nondiabetic and diabetic populations [1]. The \
first test has a state-of-the-art performance, while the second test has a \
greater uncertainty.\
\>", "Text",
 Editable->False,
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.729999760422978*^9, {3.730866937274197*^9, 3.730866937306204*^9}, {
